reviews.review_text: Recording As Crisp As A Soundboard and... A safe and reasonable performance.

ONE OF THE BEST GD AUD'S I'VE HEARD... As far as quality this is one of the best GD aud recordings I've heard.  

I usually don't bother downloading aud's but I got this one because it really feels good when listening to it. And I love the set-list !
 
I also like that you didn't delete Phil's bs'ing with the crowd to start the 2nd set. LOL !

And please, taking nothing away from Paul Tumolo because Tumolo's recordings of this show are good, but, yours (Swayne's) sound better, mainly due to how close you obviously were ? 

I noticed Paul and you used the same type of mic's. 

Anyway, I was not at this show but when I listen to it, I feel like I am there. 

Thanks and Great Job, Swayne !

Also, a special thanks to ALL of the "Swayne's, Tumolo's, and Charlie Miller's" out there on the Archive ! "The Music Never Stopped."
